      <h2>Structured Data and Schema Markup</h2>

      <p>Schema markup (JSON-LD structured data) plays a supporting role in ChatGPT citation decisions. While it is not as impactful as answer capsules or community mentions, pages with proper schema markup are cited 18% more frequently than comparable pages without it. The effect is modest but consistent across our dataset.</p>

      <p>The most impactful schema types for AI citations are:</p>

